column1: when i was stationed in vietnam in 1968  my father was also in and out of vietnam as a pilot for air america  aka the cia.  he told me one day that if i knew just 10  of what our government was doing  i d get grey hair overnight.  back then i didn t have a clue what he meant  but because my dad was a pilot in ww ii and the korean war  he began to get very cynical about our standing in the world as not being benevolent  but being malevolent.  he died a very discouraged man at age 69.  now i am 78 and i too have experienced first hand what our government is capable of  and now we are going to have that which we have done to others around the world come back to be the recipients of the evil inflicted upon us that we won t recover from.  america as a world power has faded into history.  i feel sorry for the younger ones who are going to have to live in an america that will become totally marxist or even communist in less than 5 years  if we even survive that long.
has anyone ever known someone with a mind that works as fast as   our patriot nurse  s     she is a national treasure. thank you pn . sent with love. stay safe in your travels.  michigan

it feels as if we re on the edge of a great precipice  leaning as far as we can to try and see the bottom. but most aren t noticing the ground crumbling beneath our feet. i feel in my spirit that something is coming. call it a premonition  gut feeling  hunch  or whatever  but something is on the horizon.

patriot nurse  i know full-well. i spent 10 hours in the emergency room this week  and although i feel they were thorough  ten hours was the average wait time. i had to ask my gp  who is one of the few who still listens  to run a test that the specialist i went to see ignored my request for  and he called me the next day to say that the level was so low that he was prescribing something for me right away. you end up having to do your own research and hold them accountable  or you can easily be run roughshod over in their quest to bill their 15 minutes and move on to the next one  regardless of the results.

tpn i so agree with you here.  we are teetering on a razor blade while our military is allocating 5 hours a week on training eeo  crt  wokism  transgender studies  and russian hacks are shooting up our electrical grid and evaluating our responses.  i m a retired us military combat pilot  retired 26 years    a 9 year los angeles county emergency paramedic .  we are ripe for total anarchy when the fuse it lit.  yup  i am very concerned.  i have my beans  bullets  and some bandages but i need more.   i m so ready for the rapture to come and take the believers.  i still have my buddies that are on top of what s happening in this effed up world and country and we all converse from time to time.  they too are extremely worried.   i have zero doubt the shtf scenario will strike within 24 months.  thank you for your site keep up the great work. my personal opinion is we are gonna be hit then a massive emp.  god help us should that happen.  we are lucky that we have 2 working spring water wells and both are dual usage  electric and hand pump and the water is crazy pure

ok so i m based in ontario  canada and during the summer there was a night where we were driving back from my inlaws .  the drive takes about an hour and a half and soon after we left their home i started seeing these lights in the sky that seemed really close to the ground.  the first one i saw i actually assumed was a radio pole or something but once we drove past it i realized the light wasn t attached to anything. we saw more and more of them the entire drive home and realized they were drones. we tried to rationalize what they might be doing  farmers surveilling land  etc.  even though it was fairly late at night.  we finally pulled into our town and realized that there were drones everywhere .flying all over town in circuits.  for hours that night at any given moment at least three drones could be seen within your own vicinity.  we even caught video footage and called our local police helpline to alert them of it since my bro has his drone license and i know for a fact that it s not legal where we live to have that many drones that close to each other in airspace.  we also wondered if it could be police searching for a criminal since we hadn t received an amber alert on our phones or anything.  the next night it was the same.  drones everywhere for hours.  i googled it and looked on youtube as much as i could and there were other people in two other places in canada who witnessed the same thing during the same week as us.  ottawa was one of the places.  over the course of the drive and once we got home and stood on our lawn to watch  my husband and i counted over 30 drone sightings.  keep in mind that s a distance of over 106 km  so we are talking about hundreds of drones being dispatched by some unknown source not only just over farmer s fields but over a densely populated town as well. now i m wondering if it was the ccp.anyone out there experienced something similar   anyone
